00:25:21.867 --> 00:25:23.087
<i>Tolong, lindungi dia.</i>

00:25:24.088 --> 00:25:27.076
<i>Tuhan, aku tidak mengkhawatirkan diriku sendiri.</i>

00:25:27.931 --> 00:25:30.168
<i>Aku hanya ingin menemui saudara laki-laki Shyam.</i>

00:25:30.828 --> 00:25:32.450
<i>Tolong bantu aku.</i>

00:25:41.282 --> 00:25:42.428
Chikki.

00:25:45.963 --> 00:25:46.936
Ayo.

00:25:47.695 --> 00:25:48.830
Terima kasih, Shyam.